	âˆ™	Basic: $100-150/user - Monitoring, antivirus, patch management, helpdesk (business hours)
	âˆ™	Standard: $150-200/user - Above plus backup, after-hours support, quarterly reviews
	âˆ™	Comprehensive: $200-300/user - Above plus advanced security, compliance support, strategic planning
What drives prices up:
	âˆ™	24/7 support requirements
	âˆ™	Compliance needs (HIPAA, SOC 2, etc.)
	âˆ™	Complex infrastructure (multiple locations, hybrid cloud)
	âˆ™	Legacy systems requiring specialized knowledge
