	âˆ™	Bad: Silent on data ownership and portability
	âˆ™	Better: â€œClient retains all ownership of data. MSP will provide all data in standard formats within 15 days of termination at no cost.â€
Liability caps:
	âˆ™	Bad: â€œMSP liability limited to monthly service fee.â€
	âˆ™	Better: â€œMSP liability limited to 12 months of service fees, excluding gross negligence.â€
